  "description": "<i>Dancing Summer Vacation</i> is one of a several discs with substories relating to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/tokimeki-memorial-2\">Tokimeki Memorial 2</a> romantic dating video novel simulation. Unlike the main game where focus is on romance and dating, in this set of substories, the player who is in his first year of high-school, find himself called by Miyuki, a girl from the same school, to a game of dance at the local arcade. Miyuki scores a perfect score on a DDR game and gets noticed by an interested person who summons her to participate in a tournament. All seems fine and she seems more than ready by what the player just witnessed, but the next day she calls the player to her place to show her that what she did at an arcade was just a pure luck and admits that she is no good at the game at all. Seeing a damsel in distress, the player agrees to help her get better at the game. In this side story to <i>Tokimeki Memorial 2</i> Konami mixes their dating simulation game series with their rhythm <i>Dance Dance Revolution</i> game series making this a mix of visual novel gameplay with many songs that consists of quick-time events.",
